---
// Contact section with couple's contact information
---

<section id="contact" class="content-section py-20">
	<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
		<div class="text-center mb-16">
			<div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-white/20 rounded-full mb-6 backdrop-blur-sm">
				<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path>
				</svg>
			</div>
			<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-light text-white mb-4 drop-shadow-lg">
				Contactos
			</h2>
			<div class="w-24 h-px bg-white/60 mx-auto mb-6"></div>
			<p class="text-lg text-white/90 max-w-2xl mx-auto drop-shadow-md">
				Precisam de alguma coisa ou têm dúvidas? Não hesitem em contactar-nos!
			</p>
		</div>
		
		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
			<!-- Tânia Contact -->
			<div class="bg-white/15 backdrop-blur-md rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/20 text-center hover:bg-white/20 transition-all">
				<div class="relative mb-6">
					<div class="w-24 h-24 bg-pink-400/30 rounded-full mx-auto flex items-center justify-center backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20">
						<span class="text-3xl font-bold text-white drop-shadow-md">T</span>
					</div>
				
				</div>
				
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-2 drop-shadow-md">Tânia</h3>
				<p class="text-white/80 mb-8 drop-shadow-md text-lg">A noiva</p>
				
				<div class="space-y-4">
					<a 
						href="tel:+351916702436" 
						class="flex items-center justify-center p-4 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl hover:bg-white/20 transition-all group border border-white/10"
					>
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white mr-3 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform drop-shadow-md" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path>
						</svg>
						<span class="font-medium text-white drop-shadow-md">916 702 436</span>
					</a>
					
					<a 
						href="mailto:tania@exemplo.com" 
						class="flex items-center justify-center p-4 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl hover:bg-white/20 transition-all group border border-white/10"
					>
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white mr-3 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform drop-shadow-md" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 4.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
						</svg>
						<span class="font-medium text-white drop-shadow-md">tania@exemplo.com</span>
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<!-- Miguel Contact -->
			<div class="bg-white/15 backdrop-blur-md rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/20 text-center hover:bg-white/20 transition-all">
				<div class="relative mb-6">
					<div class="w-24 h-24 bg-blue-400/30 rounded-full mx-auto flex items-center justify-center backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20">
						<span class="text-3xl font-bold text-white drop-shadow-md">M</span>
					</div>
				
				</div>
				
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-2 drop-shadow-md">Miguel</h3>
				<p class="text-white/80 mb-8 drop-shadow-md text-lg">O noivo</p>
				
				<div class="space-y-4">
					<a 
						href="tel:+351910661162" 
						class="flex items-center justify-center p-4 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl hover:bg-white/20 transition-all group border border-white/10"
					>
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white mr-3 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform drop-shadow-md" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path>
						</svg>
						<span class="font-medium text-white drop-shadow-md">910 661 162</span>
					</a>
					
					<a 
						href="mailto:miguel@exemplo.com" 
						class="flex items-center justify-center p-4 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl hover:bg-white/20 transition-all group border border-white/10"
					>
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white mr-3 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform drop-shadow-md" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 4.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
						</svg>
						<span class="font-medium text-white drop-shadow-md">miguel@exemplo.com</span>
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<!-- Footer Message -->
		<div class="mt-16 text-center">
			<div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/20 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
				<div class="flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
					<span class="text-3xl mr-2">💕</span>
					<span class="text-3xl">✨</span>
				</div>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-white mb-3 drop-shadow-md">
					Mal podemos esperar por celebrar convosco!
				</h3>
				<p class="text-white/90 drop-shadow-md">
					Obrigados por fazerem parte da nossa história de amor. 
					Até breve! 🥂
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	
	<!-- Footer -->
	<footer class="mt-20 border-t border-white/20 pt-12">
		<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
			<p class="text-white/70 drop-shadow-md">
				© 2025 | Tânia & Miguel 
			</p>
		</div>
	</footer>
</section>
